{"tid":1079714,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"中北美洲國家聯賽抽籤","createTime":"2019-03-27T06:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T14:18:04.000Z","uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9f0de3c2f5e5df2d42a82f8a98282cd1e7e18ec1","tid":1079714,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:16:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://concacafnationsleague.com/en/video/official-draw-2019-concacaf-nations-league\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fconcacafnationsleague.com%2Fen%2Fvideo%2Fofficial-draw-2019-concacaf-nations-league&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5Te9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=8abf56fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://concacafnationsleague.com/en/video/official-draw-2019-concacaf-nations-league</a><br />\n聽朝十點抽"},{"pid":"ccccfa037f6423a8e3cf4b3bbc6b09335d23d215","tid":1079714,"uid":23734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f0de3c2f5e5df2d42a82f8a98282cd1e7e18ec1","tid":1079714,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:16:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://concacafnationsleague.com/en/video/official-draw-2019-concacaf-nations-league\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fconcacafnationsleague.com%2Fen%2Fvideo%2Fofficial-draw-2019-concacaf-nations-league&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5Te9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=8abf56fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://concacafnationsleague.com/en/video/official-draw-2019-concacaf-nations-league</a><br />\n聽朝十點抽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:17:05.000Z","msg":"係咪上次講亂到仆街嗰個賽事？"},{"pid":"c6b91f06bc158580bb10f3ec9390a998ba694d3f","tid":1079714,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdXGKmZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdXGKmZ.png&h=dc41f3c8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n外圍賽前兩日踢完，分好咗3個級別<br />\nLeague A 會加埋美國、墨西哥、哥斯達黎加、巴拿馬、洪都拉斯同千里達（即係上次世界盃中北美洲外圍賽最後6強）"},{"pid":"7e8d5c35836e5ce0e36b835a8e34f4ed5ad3ceb9","tid":1079714,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://league-mp7static.mlsdigital.net/styles/image_landscape/s3/images/concacaf-nations-league-2018.png?dCgbYYYjZne9aJuT38s4LEz9InZaH014&amp;itok=IVokKnW5&amp;c=08ce797bb0b111f4ccfb5e64e152df15\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fleague-mp7static.mlsdigital.net%2Fstyles%2Fimage_landscape%2Fs3%2Fimages%2Fconcacaf-nations-league-2018.png%3FdCgbYYYjZne9aJuT38s4LEz9InZaH014%26itok%3DIVokKnW5%26c%3D08ce797bb0b111f4ccfb5e64e152df15&h=57b4ec1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>中北美洲及加勒比海國家聯賽（CONCACAF Nations League）</strong><br />\n<br />\n41個中北美洲及加勒比海足協嘅成員會參與，<span style=\"color: red;\">但危地馬拉俾FIFA ban咗，所以應該唔會2018-19年嘅CONCACAF Nations League</span><br />\n<br />\nCONCACAF Nations League制度嘅promotion同外圍賽抽籤儀式：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DzYIkCWAiRE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDzYIkCWAiRE&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5Te9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=6a1e9fb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DzYIkCWAiRE</a><br />\n<br />\n成個聯賽分League A, B, C。League A分4組，每組3隊。League B分4組，每組4隊。League C分4組，其中3組3隊，剩低一組有4隊。（<span style=\"color: red;\">喺41隊全部都會參加嘅情況之下</span>）<br />\n<br />\nLeague B, C每組首名將會升班<br />\n<br />\nLeague A, B每組包尾將會降班<br />\n<br />\nLeague A每組小組首名又係會進入最後四強淘汰賽，爭奪最後冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2018年世界盃中北美洲外圍賽最後一圈嘅六隊，即係墨西哥、哥斯達黎加、巴拿馬、洪都拉斯、美國、千里達，將會直接入League A。<br />\n<br />\n其餘CONCACAF成員將會各踢四場外圍賽（主客各二）決定League A, B, C。<br />\n<br />\n由於危地馬拉俾FIFA ban咗，所以今次嘅外圍賽將會得34隊參加。34隊先分4個Tier，Tier A同Tier D有8隊，Tier B同Tier C就會有9隊：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/193843_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F193843_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png&h=cb34855d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTier A<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/194021_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F194021_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png&h=33c9a08d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTier B<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/194116_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F194116_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png&h=b91424a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTier C<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/194253_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F194253_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png&h=67fef870&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTier D<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/194353_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F194353_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png&h=20ed0e8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外圍賽賽程<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/194432_ca3c7cfa6f486eb8568e385a03b95c3a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F194432_ca3c7cfa6f486eb8568e385a03b95c3a.png&h=5b4b0346&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想知點編嘅可以自己睇由37分開始睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n外圍賽最終排名將會決定League A, B, C<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/194629_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F194629_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png&h=57a80cda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCONCACAF Nations League外圍賽頭十名將會晉身美洲金盃決賽週<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/194757_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F194757_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png&h=f16f9d20&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6312b796a977a12d19a48a81d43265461b2c8b66","tid":1079714,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T07:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95072481c45e11b677080aeb37a80e6a4b66e053","tid":1079714,"uid":23734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6312b796a977a12d19a48a81d43265461b2c8b66","tid":1079714,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T07:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T07:22:24.000Z","msg":"中北美洲咪又係墨西哥、美國同哥斯達黎加有睇頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2073648177352d5573394bb5ce2fc17a0f900e42","tid":1079714,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T10:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82840c07c8418f4c85313af72143fb7524b7b785","tid":1079714,"uid":23889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2qpqtjj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qpqtjj.png&h=69db07b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39b2f57f9f6f09b80bf28b8c0a29174da92a980b","tid":1079714,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T14:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ea3a046c61887ba8fc2fdce5ecbf50a8732603","tid":1079714,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T15:08:02.000Z","msg":"原來英屬處女島都唔係最廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c915d7ce8a9e540d6c43addea6e7b17b47b45264","tid":1079714,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95ea3a046c61887ba8fc2fdce5ecbf50a8732603","tid":1079714,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T15:08:02.000Z","msg":"原來英屬處女島都唔係最廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T15:12:50.000Z","msg":"應該係法屬同荷屬聖馬丁島最廢，但外圍賽佢地要交手，荷屬贏咗"},{"pid":"c4ed0bc2b8263b81fa78bb32fa5a37a471da0643","tid":1079714,"uid":20284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95ea3a046c61887ba8fc2fdce5ecbf50a8732603","tid":1079714,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T15:08:02.000Z","msg":"原來英屬處女島都唔係最廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T15:20:13.000Z","msg":"排位賽抽籤有3隊pot C要對兩次pot B, 兩隊0分之一波多黎各係其中一隊, 仲要冇得對pot D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c375e22f07d7a4011b864862a1093137c881d839","tid":1079714,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T15:21:11.000Z","msg":"不過波多黎各就慘啲，同法屬聖馬丁島一樣0分，仲要做埋4零部隊，不過佢4場嘅對手都有返咁上下，只能怪抽埋啲閪籤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52fd8cdf43c2101805800ce13070e3167f3f1e42","tid":1079714,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T04:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/54798229_2308642162746583_471111586853945344_o.png?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=318ffae844b46e8c6742c2ff15736617&amp;oe=5D135681\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F54798229_2308642162746583_471111586853945344_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D318ffae844b46e8c6742c2ff15736617%26oe%3D5D135681&h=0af834cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69fa3c58bdf0e7e0d22a33bbf35742836c3a54b2","tid":1079714,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T05:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991545b9c9a16754b2db20c19d75dc1c3e396787","tid":1079714,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T14:18:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}